data.description:
Introducing Sumner Residence, a stunning 1970-built home adorned with meticulous landscaping. This abode features three spacious bedrooms and two full bathrooms. As you approach, the spacious front yard and a large carport for two vehicles.
The living room and bedrooms offer generous size, providing ample space for comfortable living. The kitchen comes equipped with a dependable oven and dishwasher. The bathrooms showcase beautifully tiled showers, adding a touch of elegance. Step outside to discover a backyard designed for entertaining, complete with outdoor bar for great entertainment. , in a sought-after neighborhood with updates and features.
Additional Property Details: 
• 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms
• Large front yard with a two-car carport
• Well-maintained landscaping
• Spacious living areas
• Updated kitchen with new granite countertops
• Versatile den that could serve as a fourth bedroom
• Recently replaced flooring (1 year ago)
• Durable metal roof (3 years old)
• Upgraded electrical system with a new breaker panel
• Proximity to the college and Altus Air Force Base
• Convenient access to various stores within walking distance
• Essential underground storm cellar, capable of accommodating up to 10 people
• Tranquil and peaceful neighborhood
• Kitchen appliances included in the sale

• Walking dish full price offer. tance to the local reservoir and park featuring a basketball court, In-ground Sprinkler system, Well, two A\cs and heater units, wit a large outdoor shed among other amenities
